        <updateDate>2021-04-07T14:12:26Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This resolution requires the chair of a House committee to administer a specific oath to any witness appearing before the committee. Currently, a committee chair is only authorized to administer an oath.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
